         <body view="all">
            <ce:sections>
               <ce:para id="p0010" view="all">This article has been retracted: please see Elsevier Policy on Article Withdrawal (<ce:inter-ref xlink:href="http://www.elsevier.com/locate/withdrawalpolicy" id="intref0010" xlink:type="simple">http://www.elsevier.com/locate/withdrawalpolicy</ce:inter-ref>).</ce:para>
               <ce:para id="p0015" view="all">This article has been retracted at the request of the Editors and the Authors as there are concerns about the reliability and validity of the results included in the article. The journal was initially contacted by the authors to request the retraction as they reported that results were not reliable due to the mistakes of detecting different metal ions in ethanol environment, which made the pH meter fail, thus making its reading inaccurate. After re-investigation, the selective detection ability of Fe<ce:sup loc="post">3+</ce:sup> was not reliable in this article. Therefore, the editors decided to retract the article. The authors apologize for any inconvenience caused.</ce:para>
